<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/3c75e4ef29234a42afac3b6665a9b26e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>颁发证书</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/0b5e5e1001ee4be08bc3176ae3073784.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>